{"tid":178870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環在線：中國富豪收購　AC米蘭擬在港上市","createTime":"2017-03-30T00:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T01:48:53.000Z","uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17ba7bf74e1781c54c5755ac2db4f62dd8379b49","tid":178870,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中環在線：中國富豪收購<br />\nAC米蘭擬在港上市</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170330/large/0330wawa_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170330%2Flarge%2F0330wawa_05.jpg&h=6a7f2c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜人民銀行副行長潘功勝批評，有啲中國資本藉住買海外球會轉移資產，話口未完，一位中國投資者得到美國對沖基金Elliott幫助下，已籌得7.4億歐元（約62億港元）收購意大利足球勁旅AC米蘭，有市場消息話，AC仲諗住喺香港上市㖭。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係成功，香港將有隻重量級足球股，AC球迷唔使再喺電視面前打氣，亦唔一定要去意大利聖西路球場朝聖，只要去買一手股票就得喇。<br />\n<br />\n嗰位收購AC嘅投資者，根據公開資料，係中歐體育投資管理長興有限公司主席李勇鴻，本身背景都有啲撲朔迷離，內地人都唔係好搞得清佢資金來源，但應該係希望藉住AC開拓中國球迷市場。<br />\n<br />\n本身李勇鴻投資過程遇到啲障礙，但經過Elliott泵水2.53億歐元後，令到單刁有機會4月中達成，《金融時報》引述接近交易嘅消息人士話，李勇鴻成功收購後，將會喺未來18個月喺港交所（388）上市。<br />\n<br />\n查實𠵱家的確係買AC嘅好時機，因為呢支傳統勁旅，過去6年喺主要歐洲賽事未試過捧盃，同時令到大股東、前意大利總理貝盧思科尼蝕大錢，咁啱中國資本又搶住買球隊，所以真係一拍即合。今次應該唔會，又臨門一腳又買唔成啩&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n李華華"},{"pid":"9c8fb291bbf52f72e95d0bcd678aa8ad2a8882c5","tid":178870,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"畀赤色資格掂親就實提早gg<br />\n曼城瀨過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa2ccbdce2dd2f2633364badd56e6a05daa17a4","tid":178870,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"Com ma star~~~~~"},{"pid":"cb6bcd0b000060aec244e39248a0e9a0c40160ca","tid":178870,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:47:36.000Z","msg":"抽"},{"pid":"ce33908cb444eb14d0b0ac8f4dd6b4c45e05ea16","tid":178870,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:01:16.000Z","msg":"其實去鄰國上仲好(如果可以)，鄰國多米蘭球迷<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，訓身撐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6479bce9df6ae28e410335e1075b56f78713e799","tid":178870,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:02:46.000Z","msg":"a米廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e35fd451ed56f637765923e964bbd610ae7f3c9","tid":178870,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"支那人咁撚有錢上咩市集資？"},{"pid":"8436628301fd27360a041ac35521d6ba58c5b096","tid":178870,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"咁即係隊波第日要睇業績，要賺錢啦<br />\n搵雲加教就啱晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424f880903a14aeb1a9e08f4ad64f8dc5da6a06a","tid":178870,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係隊波第日要睇業績，要賺錢啦<br />\n搵雲加教就啱晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫雲膠過黎教，就算年年第4有歐洲賽踢，對比番近幾季黎睇應該都好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53d80d727e3b7db4227511640a154faa5933f4c","tid":178870,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係隊波第日要睇業績，要賺錢啦<br />\n搵雲加教就啱晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家下上市邊洗要賺錢, 蝕到PK都可以上, 再蝕錢又再供股姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ef6628ab7631fa45ae8dceb19fd315d86e4ebe","tid":178870,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"乞衣糷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}